rows.body:
On your turn, other Creatures you control have an additional:
25 in all Disciplines while you control an OverWorld Creature;
"Intimidate: Energy 10" while you control an UnderWorld Creature;
"Waterproof 25" while you control a Danian Creature.
Legendary

